o.twimg.com/ext_tw_video/2052347367379423233/pu/vid/avc1/358x270/MsyQTUovWQ6TqzNM.mp4"}, "poll": false, "user": {"profilePicture": "https://pbs.twimg.com/profile_images/1734811363686662144/CY4DM_9M_normal.jpg", "displayName": "dash oner \ud83c\udf73", "username": "djdashoner"}, "content": "Oh No, LA MAGA \ud83e\udd37\u200d\u2642\ufe0f\ud83e\udd23", "parentTweet": false, "likes": 617}}, "post_flair_text": "", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "text", "uuid": "1ASsL6TFJ4", "is_twitter": false, "is_admin": false, "score": 16, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "hat", "id": 8604852, "raw_content": "Remember that government lady in white coat on TV every day: \"stay home, trust the experts, more rules for your 'safety' ?\"\n\nthat's Amy Acton, the same doc who locked down Ohio hard during covid\n\nclosed businesses, shut schools, killed dreams with one signature after another\n\nremember how it felt in your wallet? empty pockets\nmain street stores boarded up, factories quiet, families moving away\n\nsmall business with the \"closed by order\" sign\nnow she wants to be governor and she'll have bigger, statewide, long-term control\n\nHer sinister stupid plan is simple: more layers of government telling you what to do. More taxes, more bureaucrats, more \"for your own good\" controls on your life, your work, your kids. \n\nShe loved the big lockdown power trip. She'll bring back the same nanny state crap but with new paint.\n\nI was seeing Vivek Ramaswamy the other talking about he wants to shrink Ohio's 2,000 taxing authorities. What the heck, \nI didn't even know there were than many, that\u2019s way too many layers of government. We gotta shrink bureaucracy, cut red tape, and put that $$ back in our pockets.\n\nLess government sucking our money. More freedom. More jobs. Strong Ohio again.\n\nOhioans, this ain't a game. Drag your whole family, your neighbors, your coworkers to the polls in November. Vote like your kids' future depends on it, because it does.\n\nStop Amy Acton cold.\nMAGA energy in the Buckeye State. Let's go. No brakes.\n", "author": "ShiningShrine", "created": 1778171848489, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Jakylangelo", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "", "removal_source": "", "link": "", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Ohio bros, GET OUT AND VOTE NOV 2026 or Democrat \"Lockdown\" Amy Acton will become governor and turn your state into a giant prison forever", "last_comment_created": 1778174710544, "content": "<p>Remember that government lady in white coat on TV every day: &quot;stay home, trust the experts, more rules for your 'safety' ?&quot;</p>\n<p>that's Amy Acton, the same doc who locked down Ohio hard during covid</p>\n<p>closed businesses, shut schools, killed dreams with one signature after another</p>\n<p>remember how it felt in your wallet? empty pockets\nmain street stores boarded up, factories quiet, families moving away</p>\n<p>small business with the &quot;closed by order&quot; sign\nnow she wants to be governor and she'll have bigger, statewide, long-term control</p>\n<p>Her sinister stupid plan is simple: more layers of government telling you what to do. More taxes, more bureaucrats, more &quot;for your own good&quot; controls on your life, your work, your kids.</p>\n<p>She loved the big lockdown power trip. She'll bring back the same nanny state crap but with new paint.</p>\n<p>I was seeing Vivek Ramaswamy the other talking about he wants to shrink Ohio's 2,000 taxing authorities. What the heck,\nI didn't even know there were than many, that\u2019s way too many layers of government. We gotta shrink bureaucracy, cut red tape, and put that $$ back in our pockets.</p>\n<p>Less government sucking our money. More freedom. More jobs. Strong Ohio again.</p>\n<p>Ohioans, this ain't a game. Drag your whole family, your neighbors, your coworkers to the polls in November. Vote like your kids' future depends on it, because it does.</p>\n<p>Stop Amy Acton cold.\nMAGA energy in the Buckeye State. Let's go. No brakes.</p>\n", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 14, "score_up": 16, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"status": 200}, "post_flair_text": "SAVE AMERICA", "archive_id": ""}, {"is_locked": false, "tweet_id": "2052219751758442704", "sticky_comment": 0, "is_video_mp4": false, "type": "link", "uuid": "1ASsL6TFVU", "is_twitter": true, "is_admin": false, "score": 15, "suggested_sort": 0, "post_flair_class": "hunter", "id": 8604884, "raw_content": "", "author": "DingleBalls", "created": 1778173037281, "profile_picture": "", "community": "TheDonald", "ad_tier": 2, "last_comment_author": "Covfefebrulee", "is_video": false, "video_link": "", "is_new_user": false, "domain": "twitter.com", "is_crosspost": false, "preview": "https://media.scored.co/preview/1ASsL6TFVU.png", "removal_source": "", "link": "https://twitter.com/TheOfficerTatum/status/2052219751758442704", "author_flair_class": "", "is_removed": false, "media": {"resized_resolutions": [], "blurhash": "", "full_resolution": []}, "title": "Tarlov is a TDS infected clown", "last_comment_created": 1778174010582, "content": "", "score_down": 0, "author_flair_text": "", "pro_tier": 0, "is_stickied": false, "is_nsfw": false, "is_deleted": false, "is_image": false, "comments": 4, "score_up": 15, "is_edited": false, "is_moderator": false, "awards": 0, "vote_state": 2, "link_metadata": {"twitter": {"quotedTweet": false, "images": false, "linkEmbed": false, "replies": 352, "created": 1778122291000, "id": "2052219751758442704", "video": {"preview": "https